Sec. 4. ANR REPORT ON PFAS REGULATION
(a) As used in this section, “perfluoroalkyl and polyfluoroalkyl substances”
or “PFAS” means a class of fluorinated organic chemicals containing at least
one fully fluorinated carbon atom.
(b) On or before January 15, 2027, the Secretary of Natural Resources shall
submit to the House Committees on Environment and on Human Services and
the Senate Committees on Natural Resources and Energy and on Health and
Welfare a report regarding the regulation by other states of PFAS in consumer
